casebody.data:
Wednesday, July 2, 1997

MERIT DOCKET

96-2836. State ex rel. Tribble v. Turjanica.

Franklin App. No. 96APD06-797. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur. Douglas and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., would deny the motion to dismiss. On motion to expedite oral argument. Motion denied. Lundberg Stratton, J., dissents.
